text.section:
As used in this section:
"Approved company" has the same meaning as in KRS 154.27-010;
"Authority" means the Kentucky Economic Development Finance Authority established under KRS 154.20-010;
"Eligible project" has the same meaning as in KRS 154.27-010; and
"Tax incentive agreement" has the same meaning as in KRS 154.27-010.
